<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Psychology Research Study - Instructions</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Psychology Research Study</h1>
        </header>
        
        <main>
            <div class="instructions-section">
                <h2>Study Instructions</h2>
                
                <div class="instruction-content">
                    <p>In this study, you will be asked to make a decision between two financial options. Please read each option carefully before making your choice.</p>
                    
                    <div class="important-notes">
                        <h3>Important:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>There are no right or wrong answers</li>
                            <li>Please choose the option you would genuinely prefer</li>
                            <li>Take your time to read and understand each option</li>
                            <li>You will only see one decision scenario</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="process-overview">
                        <h3>What happens next:</h3>
                        <ol>
                            <li>You'll see a decision scenario with two options</li>
                            <li>Select your preferred option</li>
                            <li>Complete a brief demographic survey</li>
                            <li>Provide feedback on the study</li>
                            <li>Receive your completion code</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="navigation">
                    <a href="/experiment" class="btn btn-primary">Continue to Study</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        
        <footer>
            <p>This study is conducted by researchers at [University Name]. All responses are confidential.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>